com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.cfg

Class MutableConfigOverride

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.cfg.ConfigOverride
      • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.cfg.MutableConfigOverride
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class MutableConfigOverride
extends ConfigOverride
implements Serializable
    Extension of ConfigOverride that allows changing of contained configuration settings. Exposed to Modules that want to set overrides, but not exposed to functionality that wants to apply overrides.
    Since:
    2.8
    See Also:
